This is a statement from Koichi Takatsuki, the former chairman.

499
00:35:45,810 --> 00:35:47,562
There is also a signature and seal.

500
00:35:49,647 --> 00:35:53,150
Phew... Stupid Takatsuki is unconscious and in the hospital.

501
00:35:53,234 --> 00:35:57,280
That's just you deceiving the world.

502
00:35:59,448 --> 00:36:01,409
(Kasumi) How did you get it?

503
00:36:01,492 --> 00:36:05,163
Seriously...it was really hard.

504
00:36:06,664 --> 00:36:13,629
(Torataro) Hahahahahahahahahahahahaha...

505
00:36:14,380 --> 00:36:16,632
Haha...

506
00:36:16,716 --> 00:36:18,175
sorry

507
00:36:18,259 --> 00:36:21,596
Um... don't you know this person, Hironobu Takatsuki?

508
00:36:21,679 --> 00:36:23,055
(Male) I don't know.

509
00:36:23,139 --> 00:36:24,348
(Torataro) I'm looking for this person.

510
00:36:24,432 --> 00:36:25,349
(Female) Ah, Hironobu-san.

511
00:36:25,433 --> 00:36:26,475
Oh, do you know?

512
00:36:26,559 --> 00:36:29,395
(Woman) No, but I haven't seen you in years.

513
00:36:29,478 --> 00:36:30,563
Isn't there a photo?

514
00:36:32,648 --> 00:36:34,650
I'm looking for this person.

515
00:36:34,734 --> 00:36:39,906
(Male) I'm sure it's this person...

516
00:36:47,163 --> 00:36:50,708
Sorry! Hahahaha...

517
00:36:50,791 --> 00:36:53,669
Hironobu Takatsuki, right?

518
00:36:54,211 --> 00:36:55,546
(Hironobu) What are you?

519
00:36:55,630 --> 00:36:58,591
Do you know that your brother is in trouble?

520
00:36:59,175 --> 00:37:01,928
What's wrong with your brother?

521
00:37:02,011 --> 00:37:03,679
(Torataro) I was hospitalized due to a traffic accident.

522
00:37:03,763 --> 00:37:05,640
Please come with me!

523
00:37:06,432 --> 00:37:08,726
I need a relative to enter the hospital room.

524
00:37:09,810 --> 00:37:11,729
(Doctor) What happened? Wait a minute...

525
00:37:12,897 --> 00:37:14,649
If you do what you want, you will be in trouble!

526
00:37:14,732 --> 00:37:18,903
(Hironobu) Why is the younger brother not allowed to meet the older brother? Hey!

527
00:37:18,986 --> 00:37:20,696
(Torataro) Excuse me! Haha...

528
00:37:20,780 --> 00:37:21,614
big brother

529
00:37:22,615 --> 00:37:25,910
(Torataro) Mr. Takatsuki, I have something important to tell you.

530
00:37:26,661 --> 00:37:28,162
(Takatsuki) Hironobu?

531
00:37:28,246 --> 00:37:30,539
(Torataro) Tell me everything about this trial⸺

532
00:37:30,623 --> 00:37:34,502
I had a statement written regarding fraudulent accounting by the supporter's association.

533
00:37:43,386 --> 00:37:46,931
(Rabbitha) Second move 176th move 1 Sanka (Kyo)

534
00:37:47,682 --> 00:37:51,268
(Tatsumi) Submit Koichi Takatsuki's statement as additional evidence...

535
00:37:51,352 --> 00:37:52,186
(Tsuge) Chief Judge

536
00:37:54,397 --> 00:37:55,606
The plaintiff...

537
00:37:58,859 --> 00:38:01,028
withdraw the complaint

538
00:38:04,865 --> 00:38:08,953
Shot first

539
00:38:16,252 --> 00:38:20,840
(Reporter) Is it true that the supporter's association has committed accounting fraud? please don't run away

540
00:38:20,923 --> 00:38:23,926
Please stop recording, even recording!

541
00:38:24,010 --> 00:38:26,262
(Reporter) Mr. Tsuge Mr. Tsuge!

542
00:38:27,972 --> 00:38:30,599
(Tsuge) Recording… I hate recording.

543
00:38:30,683 --> 00:38:32,143
(Reporter) Please answer!

544
00:38:40,318 --> 00:38:42,236
thank you

545
00:38:42,320 --> 00:38:46,866
No, no, no, no, I'm really glad I made it on time.

546
00:38:46,949 --> 00:38:51,620
I believed that Kotaro-sensei would definitely make it in time.

547
00:38:53,331 --> 00:38:54,665
Oh no...

548
00:38:56,459 --> 00:38:59,545
(Kasumi) Ryumi, you chose the best move.

549
00:38:59,628 --> 00:39:03,883
(Tatsuo) Yes, I was wondering what would happen at first⸺

550
00:39:03,966 --> 00:39:07,595
Choosing Ayuda Sensei's office was really the right choice.

551
00:39:07,678 --> 00:39:11,849
Oh, I guess it wasn't just the office that I chose.

552
00:39:11,932 --> 00:39:16,270
Huh? No way, that's... eh, no, wait... let me ask you something.

553
00:39:17,146 --> 00:39:18,272
-(Kasumi) Shh... -(Tatsuo) Because...

554
00:39:18,439 --> 00:39:20,441
‪♪～

555
00:39:36,499 --> 00:39:38,459
I'm jealous of Dora

556
00:39:40,336 --> 00:39:42,421
Did you really want to eat it?

557
00:39:42,505 --> 00:39:43,464
Give me a bite

558
00:39:43,547 --> 00:39:45,674
Oh, no!

559
00:39:47,843 --> 00:39:49,637
Even if I become a lawyer⸺

560
00:39:49,720 --> 00:39:52,473
Are you focused on winning in court?

561
00:39:53,140 --> 00:39:56,519
I feel so jealous.

562
00:39:59,438 --> 00:40:03,984
(Tatsumi) Hmm...but it might be a little different.

563
00:40:07,071 --> 00:40:11,117
Unlike shogi, trials are⸺

564
00:40:12,201 --> 00:40:14,829
Just winning isn't everything

565
00:40:17,706 --> 00:40:20,668
Maybe I've started thinking like that recently.

566
00:40:23,796 --> 00:40:26,841
I feel like I understand something.

567
00:40:35,724 --> 00:40:39,436
I'll only say it once, so remember it carefully.

568
00:40:40,104 --> 00:40:42,231
What? Changed

569
00:40:44,900 --> 00:40:47,361
Can fight for someone

570
00:40:48,779 --> 00:40:52,366
Tatsumi is wonderful like that.

571
00:40:59,957 --> 00:41:01,625
-(Rabbitha) Ah-(Tatsumi) Huh?

572
00:41:02,501 --> 00:41:05,713
This is a move that is not typical of Dora, but there is a chance.

573
00:41:05,796 --> 00:41:08,340
What, you're so cunning, don't upset people.

574
00:41:08,424 --> 00:41:11,510
-(Rabbitha) I won't let you. I won't let you.-(Tatsumi) Hey, wait...

575
00:41:11,594 --> 00:41:12,761
wait a minute

576
00:41:12,845 --> 00:41:15,681
Is this a battle of impressions?

577
00:41:15,764 --> 00:41:19,226
Um, continuation of Sennichi-te

578
00:41:20,686 --> 00:41:26,984
...Or rather, it's just two close friends playing shogi together.

579
00:41:27,067 --> 00:41:29,028
laughter)

580
00:41:29,111 --> 00:41:31,030
Wow, what should I do?

581
00:41:31,113 --> 00:41:33,199
Doesn't look like Dora

582
00:41:33,282 --> 00:41:34,825
It's so sneaky...

583
00:42:00,434 --> 00:42:02,853
The lawsuit was dismissed⸺

584
00:42:02,937 --> 00:42:06,065
The weird writing is completely gone.

585
00:42:06,148 --> 00:42:09,360
(Torataro) Yeah, the disciplinary request has also been cancelled⸺

586
00:42:09,443 --> 00:42:13,530
I've heard from the bar association, so I'm relieved.

587
00:42:14,281 --> 00:42:16,033
(phone ringtone)

588
00:42:16,700 --> 00:42:20,371
Yes, Ayumu no Shogi is the Ayuta law office of losing shogi.

589
00:42:22,289 --> 00:42:28,003
What? A shogi dojo? yes yes

590
00:42:28,087 --> 00:42:29,797
‪～♪

591
00:42:29,880 --> 00:42:33,759
Ah, I see, yes, I understand.

592
00:42:33,842 --> 00:42:36,095
Yes, please come and talk to me right away.

593
00:42:36,178 --> 00:42:38,931
Yes, excuse me.

594
00:42:40,432 --> 00:42:43,227
Is it a request? He said something about shogi.

595
00:42:43,310 --> 00:42:45,729
A shogi dojo in Aifuri-cho suffered from real estate fraud⸺

596
00:42:45,813 --> 00:42:47,856
I'm in trouble because I've been asked to leave.

597
00:42:47,940 --> 00:42:50,526
It is a grave situation that the shogi dojo will disappear.

598
00:42:50,609 --> 00:42:52,236
I have to go right away

599
00:42:52,319 --> 00:42:54,363
(Torataro) Oh, wait a minute, I'll go too.

600
00:42:54,446 --> 00:42:55,906
-(Rie) This is the address.-(Tatsumi) Thank you.

601
00:42:55,990 --> 00:42:57,783
(Torataro) I'll go quickly.

602
00:42:57,866 --> 00:42:59,368
(Rie) Um, uh... when you accept...

603
00:42:59,451 --> 00:43:02,454
Well, don't forget the game fee...not the initiation fee.

604
00:43:02,538 --> 00:43:04,498
Um... ah yes ah uh...

605
00:43:04,581 --> 00:43:05,791
-(Rie) The deposit... -(Tatsumi) I'll go.

606
00:43:05,874 --> 00:43:07,251
-(Rie) Yeah, welcome.-(Torataro) I'll come.

607
00:43:08,585 --> 00:43:09,461
 (Torataro) Hey, Ryumi-sensei.

608
00:43:09,545 --> 00:43:11,422
(Tatsumi) If Torataro-sensei is coming, hurry up.

609
00:43:11,505 --> 00:43:13,590
How important is early attack?

610
00:43:13,674 --> 00:43:15,551
They say, “Don’t be on the defensive, hurry up and attack”…

611
00:43:15,634 --> 00:43:17,845
 (Torataro) Ah~ Shogi again.
